J. M. SEIDENBERG, trading and doing business as The Mayflower Plumbing Supply Co., v. MIAMI BEACH FIRST NATIONAL BANK, a Florida Banking Corporation. 18 So. (2nd) 683

June Term, 1944

July 3, 1944 Division A Rehearing Denied July 21, 1944 *656Myron H. Lewis and David B. Newsom, for appellant. Copeland, Therrell & Baisden, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

The decree appealed from is affirmed.

BUFORD, C. J., TERRELL, CHAPMAN and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
